{"tid":137430,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人有發開口夢同扯鼻鼾既屋企人","createTime":"2017-02-27T21:03:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-28T12:48:40.000Z","uid":42197,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"882509f016c5e20f6d52ad9ffafc5d4c6a8a5c50","tid":137430,"uid":42197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T21:03:34.000Z","msg":"我同阿哥既房係一間大房分做兩間<br />\n佢瞓入面果間我瞓出面<br />\n咁房之間就有道天窗俾冷氣同空氣入佢間房<br />\n而我點都夜過佢瞓因為佢要返工 我啲堂全部下晝夜晚<br />\n所以我每晚都有一個煩惱<br />\n就係佢啲鼻鼾真係好撚大聲 我成日都懷疑佢會唔會嘈醒自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲有佢係會發開口夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有次同人skype 我話我食緊芝士麵<br />\n佢竟然答我佢又食 明明佢上一秒扯緊鼻鼾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後就繼續瞓<br />\n最犀利係佢女朋友 無論我阿哥鼻鼾幾大聲 又或者發開口夢幾九唔搭八<br />\n佢都係唔會醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以 深受困擾之下 我可以點做好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c99107c9371d83e607d3d73f12956be57e139423","tid":137430,"uid":11598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T21:04:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我又食"},{"pid":"f1b7d26bbb4369d98512d01bb56d948d939f5b76","tid":137430,"uid":45185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T21:05:11.000Z","msg":"同佢同步瞓/數羊"},{"pid":"2e45bbc4289a9c6da043c75190491ca8a09f9f0e","tid":137430,"uid":42197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T21:08:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同佢同步瞓/數羊</blockquote><br />\n好難 我入睡時間比較長<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e70cf18c284303f7e15dd954bc425665a00f7b5d","tid":137430,"uid":42197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T21:10:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我又食</blockquote><br />\n果下嚇咗嚇 不過有諗過佢係咪發夢<br />\n因為又有一次佢發夢要打怪獸 點知真係一鎚打咗落佢女朋友隻手到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好似瘀咗幾日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8094a3597a5679501d67eca76d5eabd9ab3c679","tid":137430,"uid":24147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T21:11:14.000Z","msg":"全家都係咁 晚晚都交響樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n自己都係所以有免疫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ad329f33b3f3f3a03a0d4cf23677612de60ce16","tid":137430,"uid":42197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T21:12:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>全家都係咁 晚晚都交響樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n自己都係所以有免疫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁你會唔會嘈醒自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37d38335ad17072582271eb9922d981aff40768f","tid":137430,"uid":24147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T21:14:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>全家都係咁 晚晚都交響樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n自己都係所以有免疫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁你會唔會嘈醒自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔會 晚晚都好好訓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"962972325d23d65d31b62cf4ca8747986abca861","tid":137430,"uid":83941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T22:00:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a787c9391ac956bcd4ab0f0051244dd0baf25d4f","tid":137430,"uid":67761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T23:00:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我又食</blockquote><br />\n果下嚇咗嚇 不過有諗過佢係咪發夢<br />\n因為又有一次佢發夢要打怪獸 <span style=\"color: red;\">點知真係一鎚打咗落佢女朋友隻手到</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好似瘀咗幾日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b29584fbe1456c0ad7429774db0e2fb874af149c","tid":137430,"uid":6347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T23:20:33.000Z","msg":"用個銀仔掉佢之後即刻扮訓緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5aca56ead018217f74c05038d260adbb98b51d69","tid":137430,"uid":61181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T01:14:57.000Z","msg":"買舊鼻寒膠佢咬啦"},{"pid":"43b4916d89d84328aab8c3972f12be5962342703","tid":137430,"uid":42197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T10:35:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>買舊鼻寒膠佢咬啦</blockquote><br />\n其實我同佢唔係好親 佢大我十年<br />\n所以買俾佢佢應該睬我都費事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0771dcd02ac6b81d69579abf2877e9b5b17a3d99","tid":137430,"uid":42197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T10:35:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>用個銀仔掉佢之後即刻扮訓緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好高難度 會掟醒埋佢女朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc9a9c7edaa395f0c55b3cb1471e82a74cc2bb3d","tid":137430,"uid":72045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T10:41:20.000Z","msg":"同你一樣情況，最後自己去廳訓"},{"pid":"dca8e3cae7a6275ebad6baf11a9d2222664bbcd1","tid":137430,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T10:59:19.000Z","msg":"搭單問吓有冇啲耳塞係隔到鼻鼾聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1668a192427fc71ed9e07791769352814da0e8a5","tid":137430,"uid":52305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T11:05:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>搭單問吓有冇啲耳塞係隔到鼻鼾聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n五金鋪買工業用耳塞"},{"pid":"3ebb4758f529179a2180f4569b1ffe1e004a1a1c","tid":137430,"uid":74769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T12:48:40.000Z","msg":"屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我呀哥都係，有幾次第二朝返早俾佢嘈到成晚瞓唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 已經起咗身幾次拍醒佢叫佢細聲啲，轉個頭仲大聲，都唔知係咪有心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}